data.description:
Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom 2074 sq ft home nestled in a prime location that offers a perfect blend of convenience, comfort, and style. The property boasts a sprawling, fenced-in private lot, providing ample space for outdoor activities, pets, gardening, and relaxation. As you approach this residence, you'll immediately notice the fresh exterior paint, giving the home a welcoming and modern curb appeal. Step inside, and you'll discover a thoughtfully designed space, including an open loft that serves as an ideal study or home office. The heart of the home features a spacious living area with an abundance of natural light. Upstairs, 
you'll find a private primary suite complete with its own ensuite bathroom, providing a retreat-like space for relaxation. You'll also discover a balcony off the primary suite, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or evening sunsets. Recent upgrades include a brand new furnace, new garbage disposal, new outside AC condenser unit, and exterior paint. This conveniently located home in the Union School District offers a perfect blend of contemporary living, a private outdoor space, and wonderful features. It's a true gem waiting for the right owner to call it their own.
